============================环境安装==========================
    1.升级一下软件包
        yum -y update
        yum install gcc

    2.安装zlib相关依赖包  安装setuptools需要
        yum -y install zlib*

    3.ssl相关 安装pip时需要
        sudo yum install openssl-devel

    4.下载Python2.7.9，系统自带的2.6版本不能安装scrapy
        wget --no-check-certificate https://www.python.org/ftp/python/2.7.9/Python-2.7.9.tar.xz
        tar xvf Python-2.7.9.tar.xz
        cd Python-2.7.9
        ./configure
        make & make install
        修改Python软链接

        mv /usr/bin/python  /usr/bin/python.bak
        ln -s  /usr/local/bin/python2.7  /usr/bin/python

        输入python 回车查看版本

                5.编辑/usr/bin/yum
                    vim /usr/bin/yum
                    把第一行的 #!/usr/bin/python 改成 #!/usr/bin/python2.6

    6.接下来安装setuptools
        wget --no-check-certificate https://bootstrap.pypa.io/ez_setup.py
        python ez_setup.py

    7.安装pip
        wget --no-check-certificate  https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py
        python get-pip.py

    忽略[如果各种不成功可以重新编译下python]：8.编译指定： ./configure --with-zlib   --enable-optimizations


    9.安装 Twisted
        wget https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/T/Twisted/Twisted-15.2.1.tar.bz2 --no-check-certificate
        tar -xjvf Twisted-15.2.1.tar.bz2
        cd Twisted-15.2.1
        python setup.py install


    10.最后利用pip安装scrapy
        pip install scrapy

    11.pip install scrapy
        如果提示没有权限
        whereis pip 用绝对地址 install scrapy

